Aku perlu mengatur napas.

720
01:55:40,725 --> 01:55:42,269
Aku akan menyusulmu, John.

721
01:55:47,691 --> 01:55:48,733
Tidak akan.

722
01:56:00,162 --> 01:56:03,456
Kalian tentu menyadari bahwa
itu baru gelombang pertama.

723
01:56:03,540 --> 01:56:05,208
Hanya pembukaan.

724
01:56:06,084 --> 01:56:09,754
Kita bisa meneruskan ini, tapi
hanya berakhir dengan satu cara.

725
01:56:09,838 --> 01:56:11,965
Kau yakin perang
panjang itu cara terbaik?

726
01:56:12,048 --> 01:56:14,301
Tak akan ada perang panjang.

727
01:56:14,384 --> 01:56:16,720
Aku yakin kau bisa
merebut Continental.

728
01:56:16,803 --> 01:56:19,472
Tapi aku tak yakin
kau bisa menjaganya.

729
01:56:19,556 --> 01:56:22,434
Kesetiaanku lebih
dari sekadar gedung ini.

730
01:56:23,518 --> 01:56:24,936
Kami adalah High Table.

731
01:56:25,770 --> 01:56:26,897
Dan kami

732
01:56:28,190 --> 01:56:29,941
adalah Kota New York.

733
01:56:30,901 --> 01:56:32,486
Apa kita bernegosiasi?

734
01:56:36,239 --> 01:56:37,616
Aku yakin begitu.

735
01:56:43,371 --> 01:56:44,372
Perundingan?

736
01:56:45,248 --> 01:56:46,208
Perundingan.

737
01:56:50,253 --> 01:56:52,255
Apa yang kau usulkan?

738
01:56:56,510 --> 01:56:58,345
Aku mempertahankan kekuasaanku.

739
01:56:59,054 --> 01:57:00,055
Di bawah Table.

740
01:57:03,058 --> 01:57:04,226
Aku telah melayani

741
01:57:04,809 --> 01:57:09,731
serta menegakkan ketertiban dan stabilitas
untuk industri kita lebih dari 40 tahun.

742
01:57:09,814 --> 01:57:12,234
Aku mengakui bahwa
aku telah kelewatan,

743
01:57:12,317 --> 01:57:14,736
dan aku kembali bersumpah
setia pada High Table.

744
01:57:17,989 --> 01:57:19,074
Winston.

745
01:57:24,788 --> 01:57:26,373
Kau hanya menunjukkan kekuatan

746
01:57:26,456 --> 01:57:28,917
agar kami membiarkanmu
tetap di Continental.

747
01:57:32,587 --> 01:57:34,839
High Table menerima kesetiaanmu.

748
01:57:36,716 --> 01:57:38,093
Tapi bagaimana dengannya?

749
01:57:40,303 --> 01:57:43,807
Apa yang akan kita
lakukan terhadap John Wick?

750
01:57:49,521 --> 01:57:50,981
Dia harus mati.

751
01:57:52,482 --> 01:57:54,401
- Maaf, Jonathan.
- Winston!

752
01:57:54,484 --> 01:57:55,694
Tak ada cara lain.

753
01:58:07,747 --> 01:58:08,999
Baiklah, Tuan-tuan.

754
01:58:09,666 --> 01:58:12,586
Continental kini
akan dipulihkan.

755
01:58:13,712 --> 01:58:15,046
Sampai jumpa.

756
01:58:19,592 --> 01:58:20,927
Bagus, Pak.

757
01:58:56,588 --> 01:58:58,923
Berapa lama lagi
kita buka kembali?

758
01:58:59,591 --> 01:59:01,176
Seharusnya tak lama lagi.

759
01:59:05,388 --> 01:59:06,765
Tn. Wick telah pergi.

760
01:59:07,432 --> 01:59:08,933
Sungguh tragedi.

761
01:59:09,017 --> 01:59:10,352
Kau salah paham.

762
01:59:10,435 --> 01:59:12,812
Maksudku, dia
tak ada lagi di jalan.

763
01:59:13,480 --> 01:59:15,982
- Tampak mustahil.
- Tapi benar.

764
01:59:17,692 --> 01:59:20,195
Kau pasti mengerti
akibatnya jika dia selamat,

765
01:59:20,278 --> 01:59:22,447
bagi semua pihak.

766
01:59:22,947 --> 01:59:26,951
Kita tentu tak berharap Tn. Wick
mengunjungi kita di malam hari.

767
01:59:29,829 --> 01:59:31,539
Demi kebaikan kita, kuharap

768
01:59:31,623 --> 01:59:34,209
kau memastikan
ini diatasi. Mengerti?

769
01:59:34,292 --> 01:59:37,879
Tentu saja. Seberapa
jauh dia bisa pergi?

770
01:59:49,349 --> 01:59:50,517
Baba Yaga.

771
02:00:22,090 --> 02:00:23,925
Apa kabar, John?

772
02:00:24,551 --> 02:00:26,845
Kau tampak seburuk
yang kurasakan.

773
02:00:29,097 --> 02:00:31,015
Johnny.

774
02:00:31,933 --> 02:00:33,935
Angkat tangan jika
kau mendengarku, John.

775
02:00:37,021 --> 02:00:39,357
Sial. Mereka mengambil jarimu.

776
02:00:39,941 --> 02:00:41,359
Bukankah itu ironis?

777
02:00:47,907 --> 02:00:51,286
John Wick sialan.

778
02:00:51,953 --> 02:00:56,082
Jadi, pria tua itu mempertahankan
hotelnya dan kau dikorbankan.

779
02:00:56,166 --> 02:00:59,461
Aku tak menyalahkannya. Akan
kulakukan itu jika menjadi dia.

780
02:01:00,670 --> 02:01:03,256
Tapi High Table sialan ini…

781
02:01:06,217 --> 02:01:08,052
Tujuh tebasan.

782
02:01:11,556 --> 02:01:14,058
Di bawah Table hanya
ada kesengsaraan.

783
02:01:16,102 --> 02:01:19,147
Mereka akan tahu jika
kau menebas seorang raja,

784
02:01:19,230 --> 02:01:21,191
kau sebaiknya membunuhnya.

785
02:01:26,070 --> 02:01:27,405
Jadi…

786
02:01:29,866 --> 02:01:31,534
izinkan aku bertanya, John.

787
02:01:32,285 --> 02:01:33,369
Bagaimana perasaanmu?

788
02:01:35,914 --> 02:01:40,293
Karena aku sangat marah.

789
02:01:41,127 --> 02:01:42,837
Kau marah, John?

790
02:01:44,380 --> 02:01:45,381
Kau marah?

791
02:01:55,308 --> 02:01:56,935
Ya.

